  "title": "POS Z Report",
  "content": "\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hiq-page-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"hiq-t-wrap\">\r\n\t\t\r\n  \t  <div class=\"hiq-t \">\r\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"breadcrumbs\"><li><a class=\"breadcrumb-links\" hqid=\"1788908\"  href=\"/home\">Home</a></li> <li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3500940\" href=\"/omni\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Manhattan Active® Omni</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3426481\" href=\"/store-3\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Store</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"2158412\" href=\"/process-configuration-guides-3\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Process & Configuration Guides</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"2158737\" href=\"/point-of-sale\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Point of Sale</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"2225114\" href=\"/process-configuration-guides-4\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">POS Classic Guides</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3306798\" href=\"/pos-metrics-and-app-reports\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">POS Metrics and App Reports - Wiretap Strategy</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3306871\" href=\"/pos-app-reports\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">POS App Reports</a></li><li> <span>››</span>POS Z Report</li></ul>  \t\r\n\t\t<h2><a name=\"pos-z-report\" id=\"pos-z-report\"></a>POS Z Report</h2>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"info\"><ul><li><a href=\"/pos-z-report$pos-z-report\">POS Z Report</a><ul><li><a href=\"/pos-z-report$base-store-z-report\">Base Store Z Report</a><ul><li><a href=\"/pos-z-report$z-report-example\">Z Report Example</a></li><li><a href=\"/pos-z-report$z-report-field-definitions\">Z Report Field Definitions</a></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></div>\r\n\r\n<p>A retail &quot;Z Report&quot; is a summary of the transactions which occured during the course of a business day.&nbsp; &nbsp;It is called &quot;Z&quot; meaning &quot;final&quot; as it is typically generated after the store is closed so no further changes can occur on that business day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><a name=\"base-store-z-report\" id=\"base-store-z-report\"></a>Base Store Z Report</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>See the <a href=\"https://omni.helpdocsonline.com/pos-metrics-and-reporting-framework$enabling-metrics-and-z-report\">POS Metrics and Reporting guide</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With backoffice&gt;storeReportConfig settings as described, the Z report is automatically triggered by the Backoffice Store Close operation.&nbsp;&nbsp;Prior to Store Close the report is not available for a given business day.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Following Store Close the report for that day is constructed from fields as defined in the commonutil&gt;reportConfig entity, along with the configured .pdf template.&nbsp; &nbsp;An example of the base report is shown below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once the report is created, a user with appropriate <a href=\"https://omni.helpdocsonline.com/pos-resources$zreportgrant\">grant</a>&nbsp;can navigate to REPORTS menu in the Backoffice and request the report for that day.&nbsp;from those available.&nbsp;Currently the Z report is only available on behalf of the entire store, when the entire store is closed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a name=\"z-report-example\" id=\"z-report-example\"></a>Z Report Example</h4>\r\n\r\n<p><img height=\"1453\" src=\"https://dzf8vqv24eqhg.cloudfront.net/userfiles/4665/7671/ckfinder/images/qu/9401/Screenshot_2023-09-26_at_9_34_47_AM.png?Policy=eyJTdGF0ZW1lbnQiOlt7IlJlc291cmNlIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9kemY4dnF2MjRlcWhnLmNsb3VkZnJvbnQubmV0L3VzZXJmaWxlcy80NjY1Lzc2NzEvY2tmaW5kZXIvaW1hZ2VzL3F1Lzk0MDEvU2NyZWVuc2hvdF8yMDIzLTA5LTI2X2F0XzlfMzRfNDdfQU0ucG5nIiwiQ29uZGl0aW9uIjp7IkRhdGVMZXNzVGhhbiI6eyJBV1M6RXBvY2hUaW1lIjoxNzU0NzU0MDQ2fX19XX0_&Signature=kYKFEU7K5HZmc5NHb8xAnrbEnRZ1AjhxHGdyO7evZ1j-A8iPBx~BQ3HUhDfvMC8mJsFHREOI69lBPs50RufHIIUCeBqXD7rkpUGpYuVyHsSzPuR8SMU66xc0JSQpC7krgJG6zS8mnSxDBrJSBSy2xqKmQ437fapclc0SMoCNfyGFHPMsSJOPimV5tq16W6ssyoaBzaSZtrLhaPj0Kt~NCft8BvyPf2uBcXO2LTl~1hzQBnZ-AZ3HIAO145E